                     <interp inst="t18360509-1329-punishment-176" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1329-18360509 t18360509-1329-punishment-176"></join>Transported for Life</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">GEORGE DAY—
<rs id="t18360509-1329-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
